= sfFormatSize plugin =

sfFormatSize provide a helper to transform any value in bytes into something readable like kB, MB, GB, TB...
 

== Installation ==

  * Install the plugin
  
  {{{
    $ symfony plugin-install http://plugins.symfony-project.com/sfFormatSizePlugin
  }}}
  
  * Clear your cache

  {{{
    $symfony cc
  }}}  
  
=== Usage ===

  * Examples
  {{{
     <?php echo use_helper('FormatSize') ?>
     <?php $size_in_bytes = 12312443 ?>
     <?php echo format_size($size_in_bytes) ?>
  }}} 

      

=== Versions ===

1.0.0 => First version
